  "detailed_description": "Demons of Asteborg® is an action-platform game, with elements of metroidvania. Play as Gareth and prevent Zadimus from destroying Asteborg<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382790/extras/31af32479fd77ce6833fcba8e7201c1f.poster.avif?t=1630918628\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382790/extras/31af32479fd77ce6833fcba8e7201c1f.webm?t=1630918628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382790/extras/31af32479fd77ce6833fcba8e7201c1f.mp4?t=1630918628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>(illustrative image)</i><br><br>A new action platform game<br>Straight out of the 16-bit era.<br><br>Play as Gareth, a knight of the royal guard, and defeat the evil forces of Asteborg.<br>Learn powerful spells and use them to clear your path or defeat your enemies.<br>Collect gold from the remains of your opponents and purchase upgrades to unlock your full potential!<br>Prepare to face powerful bosses that will keep you on your toes.<br>Woods, mountains, swamps and more, explore the world of Asteborg and discover Gareth's mysterious past...<br>But beware, Zadimus is never far away.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382790/extras/38e51233cd9682f9ce277684946f576e.poster.avif?t=1630918628\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382790/extras/38e51233cd9682f9ce277684946f576e.webm?t=1630918628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382790/extras/38e51233cd9682f9ce277684946f576e.mp4?t=1630918628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>(illustrative image)</i>",
  "about_the_game": "Demons of Asteborg® is an action-platform game, with elements of metroidvania. Play as Gareth and prevent Zadimus from destroying Asteborg<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382790/extras/31af32479fd77ce6833fcba8e7201c1f.poster.avif?t=1630918628\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382790/extras/31af32479fd77ce6833fcba8e7201c1f.webm?t=1630918628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382790/extras/31af32479fd77ce6833fcba8e7201c1f.mp4?t=1630918628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>(illustrative image)</i><br><br>A new action platform game<br>Straight out of the 16-bit era.<br><br>Play as Gareth, a knight of the royal guard, and defeat the evil forces of Asteborg.<br>Learn powerful spells and use them to clear your path or defeat your enemies.<br>Collect gold from the remains of your opponents and purchase upgrades to unlock your full potential!<br>Prepare to face powerful bosses that will keep you on your toes.<br>Woods, mountains, swamps and more, explore the world of Asteborg and discover Gareth's mysterious past...<br>But beware, Zadimus is never far away.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382790/extras/38e51233cd9682f9ce277684946f576e.poster.avif?t=1630918628\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382790/extras/38e51233cd9682f9ce277684946f576e.webm?t=1630918628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1382790/extras/38e51233cd9682f9ce277684946f576e.mp4?t=1630918628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>(illustrative image)</i>",
